FBIS4-28182 "dreas110_c_94005" FBIS-EAS-94-110 Daily Report 6 Jun 1994 North Korea Meets With WPK Official Meets With WPK Official SK0606110294 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1039 GMT 6 Jun 94 SK0606110294 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, June 6 (KCNA) -- Secretary of the Central Committee of the Workers' Party of Korea [WPK] Hwang Chang-yop today met and had a talk with Selig Harrison, senior associate of the Carnegie Endowment for International Peace in the United States. Present on the occasion was Pak Kyong-son, a deputy department director of the Central Committee of the WPK.
